These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the turkish is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | turkish | egyptian      |
| Flower         | tulip    | dahlia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the fan of folk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | adventure    |
| Music-Genre           | metal         | folk         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, sprite
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage         | water | sprite |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Transport   | tram       | bus         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, black
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Color    | black    | orange     |
| Hobby       | camping    | gardening |
| Transport   | helicopter | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, game
2 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Cigar       | game | bolivar |
| Pet         | frog      | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

