2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie   |
| Nationality   | canadian          | nigerian   |
| Sport         | climbing     | lacrosse |

 